===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{transitive}}: To put an object into a place where it will rest.
#: ''Be sure to '''seat''' the gasket properly before attaching the cover.''
# {{transitive}}: To provide places to sit.
#: ''This classroom '''seats''' two hundred students.''

